OL,6,GSoaps and continuing dramas have a
OL,7,Gstrong relationship with their regular
OL,8,Gviewers. They are part of daily or
OL,9,Gweekly routines. Break that routine and
OL,10,Gthe bond with viewers can be broken.
OL,12,FFor some time, there has been
OL,13,Fspeculation concerning EastEnders and
OL,14,Fthe long-term decline in its ratings.
OL,16,FIn general, of course, it's important
OL,17,Fto remember that what really matters is
OL,18,Fhow many people overall see the
OL,19,Fprogramme ` including iPlayer hits `
OL,20,Fand not just the overnight ratings.
OL,3,CBBC soaps and continuing dramas:
OL,4,Cerratic scheduling and short-runs
