OL,6,FBut the BBC's scheduling of its soaps
OL,7,Fand continuing dramas has become
OL,8,Fsomewhat erratic. It isn't just an
OL,9,FEastEnders issue.
OL,11,FCasualty disappeared for several weeks
OL,12,Fduring the autumn.
OL,14,FThe revival of Waterloo Road was, in
OL,15,Feffect, the replacement for Casualty's
OL,16,Fsister programme Holby City. Its first
OL,17,Fseason has now ended after barely a
OL,18,Fmonth-and-a-half. It will return but
OL,19,Fthe date has not been confirmed.
