OL,6,FYou also wonder if Casualty could be
OL,7,Frevived if it was, once again, an
OL,8,Fannual series of ` say ` 13 episodes.
OL,10,FOf course any moves like these would be
OL,11,Fdifficult and no doubt controversial.
OL,13,FBut Is it simply the case that the
OL,14,Fmarket is saturated and that ITV has
OL,15,Fthe upper hand? Should the BBC put up a
OL,16,Fwhite flag and accept there are other
OL,17,Fways to win ratings? Or should ongoing
OL,18,Fdramas remain part of the mix as they
OL,19,Fcan connect with people the corporation
OL,20,Fsometimes struggles to reach?
